<h3>Extra Hours</h3>
<p>There will be an hourly charge of $<?php echo $extra_hours; ?> per hour for any Extra hours for Early Release Days or Snow Days. You will only be charged for the hours that are not part of the time schedule listed above. The above hours are the minimum charges/hours accepted, no refunds/rebates for early pickup.</p>
<h3>Tuition Late Fee</h3>
<p>Tuition is due on the 1st of the month. Any payments made after the first week of the month should include a $<?php echo $late_tuition; ?> late fee.</p>
<h3>After 6pm Late Fee</h3>
<p>A late pickup fee of $<?php echo $late_pickup[0]; ?> for the first ten minutes and $<?php echo $late_pickup[1]; ?> for each minute there after is payable directly to the staff person that remains at Kids-A-lot with your child in wait of your pickup.</p>
<h3>Change of Schedule Fee</h3>
<p>A $<?php echo $schedule_change; ?> Change of Schedule Administrative Fee is due when changes are made to a contract schedule. If the change is a request by Kids-A-Lot there will be no charge.</p>
<h3>Registration Fee</h3>
<p>Kids-A-lot’s $<?php echo $registration[0]; ?> annual registration fee ($<?php echo $registration[1]; ?> for infants) is non-refundable.It goes toward supplies, fees and costs needed to provide your child with a quality care program.</p>
<h3>Security Deposit</h3>
<p>At the time of enrollment the parents are required to pay the last two weeks tuition in advance. This payment is non-refundable and is credited towards your child’s last two weeks at Kids-A-lot. A month’s written notice is required so that we may fill your child’s slot. If a month’s written notice is not given the security deposit will not be credited to your child’s last month payment as stated above.</p>
<h3>Discounts</h3>
<p>Two Full Time children, 10% discount off the total tuition amount. (This is applied only when payments are on time.)</p>